{"3845640": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "我的異世界飯店", "steam_appid": 3845640, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/fd9a2726a43177af53c22517d103f43d.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一次致命事故後，你於陌生之地甦醒。女神聽見了你心中的渴望，並賜予你於充滿魔法的新世界重生的機會。她唯一的要求是——在群山之間建立一處能讓旅人與當地人安心停留的庇護所。憑藉女神的祝福與一片靜謐的土地，你的全新旅程就此展開。看哪，各式各樣的客人正逐漸填滿空蕩的房間，帶來屬於他們的故事與交流！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/e9e8675e7e2266198afd07c67be389b8.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >運用黃金、木材與石材，把你的小小飯店逐步擴建成真正壯麗的殿堂。透過充滿樂趣的小遊戲親手採集木材與石材，累積資源。解鎖全新技能、購買飯店升級項目，並重新布置房間，以迎接更多賓客。在這段旅程中，你還能與各式各樣的住客互動。隨著關係逐漸加深，他們的故事將一一展開。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/1b8ee3a12a92f4d22e1aea895219bd34.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/9e17d52bd66bc2994c058300ddcacd57.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/6348535c51439b1702d88d9d754a71cb.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/01728803c67d4a86719efa8569638e2e.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/9626c9ea812dcb52cc235c0b5e0c2820.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/72ae777bfdee009f7a14e179cb5ea38d.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>資源管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每日蒐集黃金、木材與石材，用於旅館升級。每項行動都會消耗體力，因此需要妥善規劃時間！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>趣味小遊戲</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過簡單又有趣的小遊戲來砍伐木材、開採石材，甚至偶爾擊退不守規矩的賓客。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全新技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解鎖各式技能，獲得更多體力、更快的關係提升，以及更高的資源收益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/fd9a2726a43177af53c22517d103f43d.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一次致命事故後，你於陌生之地甦醒。女神聽見了你心中的渴望，並賜予你於充滿魔法的新世界重生的機會。她唯一的要求是——在群山之間建立一處能讓旅人與當地人安心停留的庇護所。憑藉女神的祝福與一片靜謐的土地，你的全新旅程就此展開。看哪，各式各樣的客人正逐漸填滿空蕩的房間，帶來屬於他們的故事與交流！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/e9e8675e7e2266198afd07c67be389b8.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >運用黃金、木材與石材，把你的小小飯店逐步擴建成真正壯麗的殿堂。透過充滿樂趣的小遊戲親手採集木材與石材，累積資源。解鎖全新技能、購買飯店升級項目，並重新布置房間，以迎接更多賓客。在這段旅程中，你還能與各式各樣的住客互動。隨著關係逐漸加深，他們的故事將一一展開。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/1b8ee3a12a92f4d22e1aea895219bd34.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/9e17d52bd66bc2994c058300ddcacd57.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/6348535c51439b1702d88d9d754a71cb.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/01728803c67d4a86719efa8569638e2e.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/9626c9ea812dcb52cc235c0b5e0c2820.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/extras/72ae777bfdee009f7a14e179cb5ea38d.avif?t=1775548047\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>資源管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每日蒐集黃金、木材與石材，用於旅館升級。每項行動都會消耗體力，因此需要妥善規劃時間！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>趣味小遊戲</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過簡單又有趣的小遊戲來砍伐木材、開採石材，甚至偶爾擊退不守規矩的賓客。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全新技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解鎖各式技能，獲得更多體力、更快的關係提升，以及更高的資源收益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "成為異世界飯店的經理人吧！蒐集資源、挑戰趣味小遊戲、擴展你的設施，並讓賓客們賓至如歸。建立口碑，打造最頂級的異世界度假天堂！", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文, 簡體中文, 韓文, 俄文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/380ee2918aacfcb30ebc1be0660cb598b6843142/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1775548047", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/0c9fbf9b78e137de7166a3d66bf8f69f56737ab7/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1775548047", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845640/0c9fbf9b78e137de7166a3d66bf8f69f56737ab7/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1775548047", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}